<title type="html"><![CDATA[11/25(Thu.) Oriental business binge drinking/Your Extra-Bonus Vouchers (Host: Louie)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=562&amp;p=585#p585"><![CDATA[
11/25(Thu.) Oriental business binge drinking/Your Extra-Bonus Vouchers (Host: Louie)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a hybrid meeting on November 25 (Thursday):<br />On-site meeting:<br />If you have received at least one dose of vaccine, please join our physical meeting: <br />Dante coffee 丹堤(濟南店) 臺北市大安區濟南路三段25號 忠孝新生MRT Exit 3<br />On-line meeting:<br />If you haven’t gotten any vaccine or live far away from Taipei, please join our online meeting:<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ... 09#success<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1: Oriental business binge drinking: Rape claim sparks fury over China's work drinking<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-58313387">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-58313387</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1.Did you need, were you required to participate events having binge drinking? Do you enjoy it?<br />2.Were you badly drunken before? What was that occasion? Please share us your story.<br />3.Were you coerced to drink excessively? What do you usually do to avoid over-drinking at the event?<br />4.People go blunt, candid and even touchy-feely when getting tipsy or drunk. Do you like the feel yourself? Do you think people take some advantage while pretending drunk?<br /><br />Session 2: Your Extra-Bonus Vouchers<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://news.immigration.gov.tw/NewsSection/Detail/be0c2584-41da-4786-8186-0d36f03c73e0?category=0&amp;lang=EN">https://news.immigration.gov.tw/NewsSec ... =0&amp;lang=EN</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1.All 8 kinds of extra-bonus vouchers associated to the quintuple stimulus voucher event had completed lucky-draws by 11/5. Did you join the lucky-draw and were you lucky enough to win? Which one did you win?<br />2.Have you used your extra-bonus voucher as yet? What is your plan for it?<br />3.Which one of those 8 sorts of bonus vouchers is your favorite (even you didn’t win the draw)? Why?<br />4.Please share us your experience attending these kinds of recreational activities. What makes you so fond of?<br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.丹堤咖啡有100元低消喔!<br />2.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Tue Nov 16, 2021 8:28 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
